@node "install" "Installation"
[ Installation ]

Just copy the animation icon to the drawe "images" in the Ibrowse directory.
@endnode

@node "intro" "Introduction"
[ Introduction ]

This animation has been made to be utilized with Ibrowse, a famouse HTTP
browser for the Amiga computer. It shows an Amiga Logo. When Ibrowse is
establishing a connection, the red cube over the 'i' starts rotating while
the logo is zoomed in and out.
@endnode

